<p><strong>Ranges</strong> from Whirlpool, Maytag, and KitchenAid appear regularly in S&amp;D stores. Slide-in models with convection ovens carry the highest retail prices and therefore the largest discounts &mdash; $300 to $800 off in many cases.</p>

